{
  "texts": [
    "In this way, deepfakes further threaten knowledge by discouraging the formation of true beliefs based on video footage.",
    "In short, deepfakes pose a three-pronged threat to knowledge acquisition from video footage.",
    "Put differently, deepfakes threaten the ability to acquire knowledge by seeing for oneself through video footage.",
    "It is widely hoped that the three-pronged threat resulting from advancements in the development of realistic deepfakes can be countered by advancements in automated deepfake detection technologies (ADDs).",
    "ADDs might in principle be used to help remove deepfakes from various online environments, or to label videos as authentic or inauthentic."
  ]
}